14#ifndef API_JSEP_ICE_CANDIDATE_H_
15#define API_JSEP_ICE_CANDIDATE_H_
16
17#include <stddef.h>
18
19#include <memory>
20#include <string>
21#include <vector>
22
23#include "api/candidate.h"
24#include "api/jsep.h"
25#include "rtc_base/constructor_magic.h"
26#include "rtc_base/system/rtc_export.h"
27
28namespace webrtc {
29
30// Implementation of IceCandidateInterface.
31class RTC_EXPORT JsepIceCandidate : public IceCandidateInterface {
32 public:
33 JsepIceCandidate(const std::string& sdp_mid, int sdp_mline_index);
34 JsepIceCandidate(const std::string& sdp_mid,
35 int sdp_mline_index,
36 const cricket::Candidate& candidate);
37 JsepIceCandidate(const JsepIceCandidate&) = delete;
38 JsepIceCandidate& operator=(const JsepIceCandidate&) = delete;
39 ~JsepIceCandidate() override;
40 // |err| may be null.
41 bool Initialize(const std::string& sdp, SdpParseError* err);
42 void SetCandidate(const cricket::Candidate& candidate) {
43 candidate_ = candidate;
44 }
45
46 std::string sdp_mid() const override;
47 int sdp_mline_index() const override;
48 const cricket::Candidate& candidate() const override;
49
50 std::string server_url() const override;
51
52 bool ToString(std::string* out) const override;
53
54 private:
55 std::string sdp_mid_;
56 int sdp_mline_index_;
57 cricket::Candidate candidate_;
58};
59
60// Implementation of IceCandidateCollection which stores JsepIceCandidates.
61class JsepCandidateCollection : public IceCandidateCollection {
62 public:
63 JsepCandidateCollection();
64 // Move constructor is defined so that a vector of JsepCandidateCollections
65 // can be resized.
66 JsepCandidateCollection(JsepCandidateCollection&& o);
67 // Returns a copy of the candidate collection.
68 JsepCandidateCollection Clone() const;
69 size_t count() const override;
70 bool HasCandidate(const IceCandidateInterface* candidate) const override;
71 // Adds and takes ownership of the JsepIceCandidate.
72 // TODO(deadbeef): Make this use an std::unique_ptr<>, so ownership logic is
73 // more clear.
74 virtual void add(JsepIceCandidate* candidate);
75 const IceCandidateInterface* at(size_t index) const override;
76 // Removes the candidate that has a matching address and protocol.
77 //
78 // Returns the number of candidates that were removed.
79 size_t remove(const cricket::Candidate& candidate);
80
81 private:
82 std::vector<std::unique_ptr<JsepIceCandidate>> candidates_;
83
84 RTC_DISALLOW_COPY_AND_ASSIGN(JsepCandidateCollection);
85};
86
87} // namespace webrtc
88
89#endif // API_JSEP_ICE_CANDIDATE_H_
